  <summary date="2024-02-05T16:50:13Z" status="Introduced in House">Preventing Private Paramilitary Activity Act of 2024

This bill establishes a federal statutory framework to prohibit certain conduct involving actions as a part of a (or on behalf of) a private paramilitary organization while armed.

An individual who violates the prohibition is subject to criminal penalties. The bill also authorizes civil remedies.</summary>
